{"content": "I need to multiply a12 \u00d7 887 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert a12 (base 11) to base 10**\n- a12\u2081\u2081 = 10\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- = 10\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- = 1210 + 11 + 2\n- = 1223\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 887 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 887\u2081\u2081 = 8\u00d711\u00b2 + 8\u00d711\u00b9 + 7\u00d711\u2070\n- = 8\u00d7121 + 8\u00d711 + 7\u00d71\n- = 968 + 88 + 7\n- = 1063\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 1223 \u00d7 1063 = 1,300,049\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 1,300,049 (base 10) to base 11**\n- 1,300,049 \u00f7 11 = 118,186 R 3\n- 118,186 \u00f7 11 = 10,744 R 2\n- 10,744 \u00f7 11 = 976 R 8\n- 976 \u00f7 11 = 88 R 8\n- 88 \u00f7 11 = 8 R 0\n- 8 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 8\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 808823\n\n**Answer: 808823**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 411}